FBIS4-8416 "dreeu071_i_94028" FBIS-EEU-94-071 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Three Killed in Shelling of Usora Three Killed in Shelling of Usora LD1304140694 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 1300 GMT 13 Apr 94 LD1304140694 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Excerpts] The Serbs have resumed their attacks on Usora. Three people have been killed, including one child, and six civilians wounded in Serb artillery attacks on the residential areas of the free Croat community of Usora over the last 24 hours. [passage omitted] A general alert was sounded again this morning when four shells landed on the free territory of Usora. Fortunately, there were no casualties.
